                            <comment id="105008" author="olivergierke" created="Fri, 27 Jun 2014 09:48:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Turns out this was unrelated to &lt;tt&gt;@EnableMongoAuditing&lt;/tt&gt;. Our serialization customizations were trying to find properties by their JSON names. You &lt;tt&gt;PetFood&lt;/tt&gt; only has renamed fields, so that not a single property could be found which made Jackson complain that it&apos;s got nothing to serialize.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should be fixed in master and the bugfix branch. Feel free to give the snapshots a try.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="105172" author="ncantelmo" created="Tue, 1 Jul 2014 10:42:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I just tested it out with the release version and it&apos;s working as expected now.  Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
